title: Star Wars - The Clone Wars Complete
description:
Star Wars - The Clone Wars Complete

110 Episodes | HDTV | AVI + MP4 | 18.9 GB Total 


In 2013, the television series was pulled from Cartoon Network after airing its fifth season, making Season Five the final season of Star Wars: The Clone Wars. 

THE GOOD NEWS............

Star Wars: The Clone Wars Supervising Director Dave Filoni announced via Facebook on October 11, 2013 that fans will get to see the full 22 episode Season 6 in early 2014, with an episode that includes Master Yoda's most dangerous mission. It was not revealed where these episodes will air, if they will debut on Disney XD, or if they will only be made available on a streaming platform.

Season 1 - 22 Episodes - AVI
Season 2 - 22 Episodes - AVI
Season 3 - 23 Episodes - AVI
Season 4 - 23 Episodes - AVI
Season 5 - 20 Episodes - MP4 
Season 6 - To be released early 2014
